---
title: Breaded Shrimp Platter with Seasoned Wedges and Cheesy Zucchini Coins
description: Finger food at it's finest – may we present you with our Breaded Shrimp Platter! Panko-crusted shrimp gets served up with mind-blowing Parmesan-coated zucchini coins and chicken-salted potato wedges. Wash those hands and dig in!
